{"tid":128094,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（射擊）殺曱甴方法集思廣益","createTime":"2017-02-20T14:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T00:17:54.000Z","uid":6116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a2b047e876ae58d4a4c98bf55371943a60ed65c","tid":128094,"uid":6116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"利申自己係好驚曱甴的<br />\n<br />\n最近鄰居裝修走左好多曱甴過黎 隻隻成隻手指咁長 所以想推薦一個好用既方法<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5y1Ts10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5y1Ts10.jpg&h=a1b885d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要記住 一定要用滴露 威路士係唔work 的<br />\n滴露同水比例大概一比五左右就ok <br />\n包你射幾槍隻野就反肚 <br />\n一黎殺蟲水貴對人體有害 二黎滴露個個都有支係屋企 搞掂用掃把掃左佢就ok 保持距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望幫到一d同我一樣驚曱甴既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f10dd5cf21e52f6c007dba4148ee2eba67eaf59","tid":128094,"uid":10011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:19:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6be93aefaf158eff3bcca1b420f279b076b186c3","tid":128094,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:20:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2bc993c20dd5caea6b8f252667eab11e4e16703","tid":128094,"uid":57548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"大叫呀媽"},{"pid":"c9bffd8cf0664022caec6f567fd523230418e45e","tid":128094,"uid":6116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/20/222043_a1de131b7bb365a06d2bec8fd4db8848.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F20%2F222043_a1de131b7bb365a06d2bec8fd4db8848.jpg&h=a99494fe&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢把野係吸死左定未死的？"},{"pid":"ccc29de8999e5d9ed18050dabe0485b33a2ffc39","tid":128094,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT